title: Omni-Directional Conveyor System
---
Modular omnidirectional conveyor system detecting conected cells and and determining item drop off locations.

This system uses electrical signals to detect connected cells steming from an origin cell. Once detected cells can cominicate to and from the origin cell allowing for users to select any space connected to a cell for item dropoff. Users can use a fiducial attached to the item to set the drop off point of all items of the same fiducial value. After set up all fiducials with set values will be routed to the user specified location as they are tracked over the conveyor. 

